## Debugging

### 1. Ver logs en Supabase

```sql
SELECT fuente, status, error_message, duration_ms
FROM LOG_SCRAPING
ORDER BY created_at DESC
LIMIT 10;
```

### 2. Ver metadata detallada

```sql
SELECT 
  fuente,
  status,
  metadata->>'source_json_ld' as has_json_ld,
  metadata->>'source_claude' as claude_fields,
  duration_ms
FROM LOG_SCRAPING
WHERE fuente = 'computrabajo'
ORDER BY created_at DESC
LIMIT 5;
```

### 3. Identificar portales problemáticos

```sql
SELECT 
  fuente,
  COUNT(*) as attempts,
  SUM(CASE WHEN status = 'success' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as successes,
  ROUND(100.0 * SUM(CASE WHEN status = 'success' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) / COUNT(*)) as success_rate
FROM LOG_SCRAPING
GROUP BY fuente
ORDER BY success_rate ASC;
```

